# Polymarket trades Analyze

> Analyze trading behavior like never before!

## Brief overview
The goals was to be able to analyze returns and traits of people on the platform Polymarket. It turned out to be way more complex than expected.

Getting the data requires sql calls to Bigquery to access the Public Dataset. Creating the query took research.

Then the dataset was built with thousands of queries like this one... But that was the encrypted dataset...

In order to decrypt it took in depth knowledge in the workings of Polymarket.

Then we had a raw dataset. We needed to follow the research we'd read and create predictors! These are metrics which summarise a person behaviour
i.e. their general risk tolerance.

Only once that was done, we could do some modeling, which we did as much as could be done!
 


```
                                    +-------------+
                                    |             |
                                    |   Trading   |
                                    |   Analysis  |
                                    |   Engine    |
                                    |             |
                                    +------+------+
                                           
                                           
                                           
   +------------+    +-------------+    +--+-------+    +--------------+
   |            |    |             |    |          |    |              |
   | Raw Market +---->  Process    +---->  Analyze +---->  Visualize   |
   |    Data    |    |   Data      |    |  Trades  |    |   Results    |
   |            |    |             |    |          |    |              |
   +------------+    +-------------+    +----------+    +--------------+
```

## How it works!

- **Data Processing**: Import and process trading data from GOOLGE and save to csv (Runtime - 2 Hours)
- **Trader Analysis**: Evaluate individual trading behaviors with 40+ metrics (Runtime - 10 hours)
- **Portfolio Tracking**: Monitor stock prices and portfolio performance (Instant)
- **Visualization**: Generate graphs and visual representations of trading patterns (runtime - 20 minutes)
- **Advanced Metrics**: Calculate everything from basic returns to complex behavioral indicators (Instant)

